HEADWORD: flameproof
<hw>flameproof</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>not susceptible to burning;
noncombustible; fireproof; -- of artifacts. Opposite of
<ant>combustible</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> flame-retardant.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

